s law and the meanings of 'home' and 'institution' it proposes solutions to the Cheshire West ruling's paradoxical implications.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2023) 0aDetention of personszGreat Britain. 0aPeople with disabilitiesxLegal status, laws, etczGreat Britain. 0aPeople with disabilitiesxLegal status, laws, etc.zGreat Britain. 0aSocial servicezGreat Britain. 7aLAW / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311119677040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781529212006zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781529212006/original  a978-3-11-119677-0 Bristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA